text: Ángel Aldama (born 6 June 1936) is a Guatemalan wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Guatemalan male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Guatemala Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Zacapa Department
